x\geq y\geq z\geq 0:
\sum_{x,y,z}\frac{x}{\sqrt{x+y}}\geq \sum_{x,y,z}\frac{y}{\sqrt{x+y}}
x^2+y^2+z^2=1
a=\sqrt{y+z},b=\sqrt{z+x},c=\sqrt{x+y}
c\ge b \ge a \ge 0
x=\frac{b^2 + c^2 - a^2}{2},y=\frac{c^2 + a^2 - b^2}{2},z=\frac{a^2 + b^2 - c^2}{2}.
\sum_{a,b,c} \frac{b^2 + c^2 - a^2}{2c} \ge \sum_{a,b,c} \frac{c^2 + a^2 - b^2}{2c},
x\ge y\ge z \ge 0
y+z>0.
x\ge y\ge z.
\sum_{x,y,z}\frac{x}{\sqrt{x+y}}- \sum_{x,y,z}\frac{y}{\sqrt{x+y}}\\= \frac{x}{\sqrt{x+y}}+\frac{y}{\sqrt{y+z}}+\frac{z}{\sqrt{z+x}}-\frac{y}{\sqrt{x+y}}-\frac{z}{\sqrt{y+z}}-\frac{x}{\sqrt{z+x}}\\=\frac{x-y}{\sqrt{x+y}}+\frac{y-z}{\sqrt{y+z}}-\frac{x-z}{\sqrt{z+x}}\\=\frac{x-y}{\sqrt{x+y}}+\frac{y-z}{\sqrt{y+z}}-\frac{x-y}{\sqrt{z+x}}-\frac{y-z}{\sqrt{z+x}}\\=(x-y)\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{x+y}}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{z+x}}\right) + (y-z)\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{y+z}}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{z+x}}\right)\\=(x-y)\frac{\sqrt{z+x}-\sqrt{x+y}}{\sqrt{x+y}\sqrt{z+x}} + (y-z)\frac{\sqrt{z+x}-\sqrt{y+z}}{\sqrt{y+z}\sqrt{z+x}}\\=(x-y)\frac{z-y}{\sqrt{x+y}\sqrt{z+x}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{x+y})} \\+ (y-z)\frac{x-y}{\sqrt{y+z}\sqrt{z+x}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{y+z})} \ge 0 \\ \Leftrightarrow  \sqrt{x+y}\sqrt{z+x}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{x+y})\ge \sqrt{y+z}\sqrt{z+x}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{y+z}) \\ \Leftrightarrow  \sqrt{x+y}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{x+y})\ge \sqrt{y+z}(\sqrt{z+x}+\sqrt{y+z})  
